  <title class="- topic/title ">Changing Campaign Status</title>
  <shortdesc class="- topic/shortdesc ">You can use the iPhone app to change
	 the active/inactive status of a campaign. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody class="- topic/body task/taskbody ">
    <steps id="steps_D60F257D36AB493D99B1AC4EA3B8B393" class="- topic/ol task/steps ">
      <step id="step_409A05491F8C4E6E94E31DB9C0821BD6" class="- topic/li task/step ">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Start the app, then press the name of
			 the campaign you want to view. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
          <p class="- topic/p ">The app opens to show your active campaigns.
				Press 
				<uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">All
				  Campaigns</uicontrol> to view all active and inactive campaigns. 
			 </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_7C237FF073084CD2ACC7A6A4ABED0184" class="- topic/li task/step ">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Press 
			 <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Details</uicontrol>. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult class="- topic/itemgroup task/stepresult ">
          <p class="- topic/p ">The Details screen for the campaign opens. 
			 </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_C44E219A8987427396424C06DD9BAE20" class="- topic/li task/step ">
        <cmd class="- topic/ph task/cmd ">Press 
			 <uicontrol class="+ topic/ph ui-d/uicontrol ">Change</uicontrol>,
			 then confirm that you want to deactivate or activate the campaign. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
